{"type":"message","id":"b4488c6f","parentId":"6035566b","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:38:07.675Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if they could create a Google account for me and connect it so I can create Google Calendar events for every task. Let me think about this...\n\nOpenClaw has integrations and tools. Let me think about what's available. I don't have a direct Google Calendar tool listed in my available tools. But OpenClaw might support some integrations.\n\nLet me think about what's possible:\n1. The user could create a Google account and potentially connect it via OAuth\n2. OpenClaw might have Google Calendar integration\n3. I could potentially use the browser to interact with Google Calendar\n\nLet me be honest about what I know and don't know. I don't have a specific Google Calendar tool, but OpenClaw might support it as an integration. \n\nI should check the documentation to see if Google Calendar integration is available, or be transparent about what's actually possible here.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Boa pergunta. A resposta curta é: **provavelmente sim, mas com algumas ressalvas**.\n\nDeixa eu quebrar:\n\n---\n\n### ✅ O que é possível\n\n- **Criar uma conta Google pra mim** — totalmente viável. Uma conta dedicada tipo `coda@gmail.com` ou similar.\n- **Conectar ao OpenClaw** — o OpenClaw suporta integrações via OAuth. Se tiver integração nativa com Google Calendar, você autenticaria essa conta lá e eu passaria a ter acesso.\n- **Criar eventos automaticamente** — uma vez conectado, eu poderia criar, listar e editar eventos via API do Google Calendar.\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ O que eu não sei ainda\n\nNão tenho certeza se o OpenClaw já tem integração nativa com Google Calendar \"de fábrica\" ou se precisaria de configuração manual (via API key + OAuth). Deixa eu checar a documentação:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01DRdzvEN385RbJdnsfXYuMA","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":10,"output":582,"cacheRead":15130,"cacheWrite":270,"totalTokens":15992,"cost":{"input":0.00003,"output":0.00873,"cacheRead":0.004539,"cacheWrite":0.0010125,"total":0.0143115}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771994274807}}
